SHADOW JUMPER raced close to the pace inside, was crowded and steadied past the gap, awaited room on the turn and lacked a stretch response. STORMING PEACE broke in, was crowded and bumped past the gap, stalked to the turn and gave way. UNBRIDLED DIVA showed good early speed, was crowded and bumped past the gap and was through early. Following a stewards' inquiry, SOCIAL CLUB was disqualified and placed ninth for causing interference on the backstretch.
